Vietnam to launch fund for victims of war-era defoliant
HANOI, Vietnam (AP) _ Vietnam is launching a support fund forvictims of the defoliant Agent Orange, more than two decades afterits use by U.S. forces in the Vietnam War, the Labor newspaperreported Saturday.
